  "Brain1 NV" = "#ED9F9B",
  "Brain1 SF" = "#E5A79A",
  "Brain2 NV" = "#F1D0C6",
  "Brain2 SF" = "#6E8FB2",
  "Brain3 NV" = "#8AB1D2",
  "Brain3 SF" = "#A6CDE4",
  "Brain4 NV" = "#D0E0EF",
  "Brain4 SF" = "#74B69F",
  "Brain5 NV" = "#80BA8A",
  "Brain5 SF" = "#9CD1C8",
  "Lung NV" = "#F1DFA4",
  "Lung SF" = "#CC88B0"
)
# Load the data
load("merged_10Brain_Lung.RData")
data <- merged_10Brain_Lung@meta.data[, c("nCount_RNA", "nFeature_RNA", "orig.ident")]
# Show the figure
p<- ggplot(data, aes(x = nCount_RNA, y = nFeature_RNA, color = orig.ident)) +
  stat_smooth(method = "loess", se = FALSE, size = 1.2)+
  labs(x = "number of UMI", y = "number of genes") +
  scale_color_manual(values = custom_colors) +
  theme_minimal() +
  theme_prism(base_size = 15) +
  theme(
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5, size = 20, face = "bold"),
    axis.title = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold"),
    axis.text = element_text(size = 15, face = "bold"),
    legend.text = element_text(size = 12, face = "bold"),
    plot.margin = margin(25, 25, 25, 25)
  ) +
  guides(color = guide_legend(
    title = "Platform",
    title.theme = element_text(size = 13, face = "bold"),
    label.theme = element_text(size = 12, face = "bold")
  ))

Figure 1 (D)

# Load the library
library(eulerr)
library(grid)
# Load the data
load("merged_all.RData")
nv_cells <- rownames(merged_R_9_24h_2@meta.data)[merged_R_9_24h_2@meta.data$orig.ident == "Lung NV"]
sf_cells <- rownames(merged_R_9_24h_2@meta.data)[merged_R_9_24h_2@meta.data$orig.ident == "Lung SF"]
nv_barcodes <- gsub("Lung NV_", "", nv_cells)
sf_barcodes <- gsub("Lung SF_", "", sf_cells)
shared <- length(intersect(nv_barcodes, sf_barcodes))
total_nv <- length(nv_barcodes)
total_sf <- length(sf_barcodes)
total <- total_nv + total_sf - shared  
data <- c(
  "Lung NV" = total_nv - shared,
  "Lung SF" = total_sf - shared,
  "Lung NV&Lung SF" = shared
)
labels <- c(
  paste0(data["Lung NV"], "\n(", signif(data["Lung NV"] / total * 100, 4), "%)"), 
  paste0(data["Lung SF"], "\n(", signif(data["Lung SF"] / total * 100, 4), "%)"),
  paste0(data["Lung NV&Lung SF"], "\n(", signif(data["Lung NV&Lung SF"] / total * 100, 4), "%)")
)
# Show the figure
venn <- euler(data)
plot(
  venn,
  fills = list(fill = c("#F9DF91", "#A8CFE8", "#E6D9AE"), alpha = 0.7),
  edges = NULL,
  labels = FALSE,
  main = list(label = "Lung", cex = 4, font = 2),
  quantities = FALSE
)
grid.text(labels[1], x = 0.12, y = 0.5, gp = gpar(fontsize = 20, fontface = "bold")) 
grid.text(labels[2], x = 0.88, y = 0.5, gp = gpar(fontsize = 20, fontface = "bold"))
grid.text(labels[3], x = 0.5, y = 0.5, gp = gpar(fontsize = 40, fontface = "bold"))

Figure 1 (E)

# Load the data
meta <- merged_R_9_24h_2@meta.data
nv_cells <- rownames(meta)[meta$orig.ident == "Lung NV"]
sf_cells <- rownames(meta)[meta$orig.ident == "Lung SF"]
nv_barcodes <- gsub("Lung NV_", "", nv_cells)
sf_barcodes <- gsub("Lung SF_", "", sf_cells)
shared_barcodes <- intersect(nv_barcodes, sf_barcodes)
nv_only_barcodes <- setdiff(nv_barcodes, shared_barcodes)
sf_only_barcodes <- setdiff(sf_barcodes, shared_barcodes)
nv_only_cells <- paste0("Lung NV_", nv_only_barcodes)
sf_only_cells <- paste0("Lung SF_", sf_only_barcodes)
shared_nv_cells <- paste0("Lung NV_", shared_barcodes)
shared_sf_cells <- paste0("Lung SF_", shared_barcodes)
df <- data.frame(
  Cell_Group = c(
    rep("Lung NV unique", length(nv_only_cells)),
    rep("Shared", length(shared_nv_cells) + length(shared_sf_cells)),
    rep("Lung SF unique", length(sf_only_cells))
  ),
  Gene_Count = c(
    meta[nv_only_cells, "nFeature_RNA"],
    meta[c(shared_nv_cells, shared_sf_cells), "nFeature_RNA"],
    meta[sf_only_cells, "nFeature_RNA"]
  ),
  UMI_Count = c(
    meta[nv_only_cells, "nCount_RNA"],
    meta[c(shared_nv_cells, shared_sf_cells), "nCount_RNA"],
    meta[sf_only_cells, "nCount_RNA"]
  )
)
bar_colors <- c("#F9DF91","#E6D9AE","#A8CFE8") 
df$Cell_Group <- factor(df$Cell_Group, levels = c("Lung NV unique", "Shared", "Lung SF unique"))
gene_medians <- tapply(df$Gene_Count, df$Cell_Group, median)
overall_gene_median <- median(df$Gene_Count)
# Show the figure
par(xpd = F)
par(mar = c(5, 8, 5, 5))
bp <- barplot(
  gene_medians,
  beside = TRUE,
  col = bar_colors,
  ylab = "Median gene count per cell",
  cex.main = 1.6, 
  cex.axis = 1.2, 
  cex.lab = 1.2,
  las = 2, 
  font.lab = 2,
  names.arg = FALSE,
  font.axis = 2,
  font.main = 2
)
text(
  x = bp, 
  y = par("usr")[3] - 0.05 * diff(par("usr")[3:4]), 
  labels = names(gene_medians), 
  srt = 25, 
  adj = 1, 
  xpd = TRUE, 
  cex = 1.1,
  font = 2
)
abline(h = overall_gene_median, lty = 2, col = "red", lwd = 2)
par(xpd = TRUE)
text(x = max(bp) - 1, 
     y = overall_gene_median+30, 
     labels = "", 
     col = "red",
     cex = 1.5)
gene_se_median <- tapply(df$Gene_Count, df$Cell_Group, function(x) mad(x) / sqrt(length(x)))
arrows(
  x0 = bp, 
  y0 = gene_medians - gene_se_median, 
  x1 = bp, 
  y1 = gene_medians + gene_se_median, 
  angle = 90, 
  code = 3, 
  length = 0.1, 
  lwd = 1.3
)
